(click: "family")[$t[We raised Belona as if she were (link-reveal: "our own")[$t[, because she *was* our own]].] (click: "was")[$t[I saw her at the school that day and I saw myself.] (live: 2s)[(stop:)$t[We talked.] (live: 2s)[(stop:)$t[She told me that her family had died in the Takeover(click: "died")[$t[, that she had seen]].]]]] (click: "seen")[$t[Sometimes there’s so much cruelty in the world…]]

](click: ?her)[$t[She was very withdrawn.]] (click: "nothing")[$t[I don’t remember |her>[her] having any friends.] (click: "withdrawn")[$t[The neighbors lent her books and she devoured them.]] (click: "books")[$t[She didn’t do particularly well in class.]] (click: "particularly")[$t[Not bad either.]]

](click: "neighbors")[$t[She barely left home.] (live: 1s)[(stop:)$t[She remembered little of the City.]] (click: "little")[$t[I think she never appreciated the freedom we had in Claro Largo(click: "never")[$t[ because she didn’t know what it was for it to be taken away from you]].]]

]<center>prayed(click-replace: "prayed")[$tr[Belona] prayed $tr[often.]] (click: "often")[$t[I believe that’s what she did.]] (click: "believe")[$t[Generally in Claro Largo we liked it when kids nurtured their faith from an early age(click: "faith")[$t[, but the way Belona described her inner revelations disturbed us a bit]].]] (click: "revelations")[$t[I think she understood the concept of talking to God(click: "understood")[$t[, but she sat by herself, in contemplation, without talking to anyone]].]] (click: "contemplation")[$t[That’s what she said at least.]] (click: "she said")[$t[I guess she *had* to be talking with someone, with herself, or her family.]]</center>
(click: "cruelty")[$t[She described it as exploring her own being.]] (click: "described it")[$t[When you asked for a clearer explanation, she talked of burying her hands in her guts looking for something fundamental(click: "something")[$t[, or looking for |herself>[herself]]].]] (click: ?herself)[$t[Once I asked her if she had ever *found* herself.]] (click: "found")[$t[She |told>[told] me she had found there was nothing to *be* found.]] (click: ?told)[$t[Many of these conversations I didn’t share with the rest of the elders.]] (click: "elders")[$t[They suspected enough already.]]

(click: "freedom")[$t[I |tried>[tried] to pray with her.]] (click: ?tried)[$t[Several times over the course of (link-reveal: "a month")[$t[ or nearly a month]].]] (click: "nearly")[$t[Then I stopped.] (live: 1s)[(stop:)$t[I didn’t like it, to be honest.]]] (click: "honest")[$t[The last time, I think I got some of what Belona was |talking>[talking] about.]] (click: ?talking)[$t[(link-reveal: "Looking for yourself…")[ $t[I expected touching my guts to be more metaphorical(click: "expected")[$t[, but I |felt>[felt] it]].]]]] (click: ?felt)[$t[I felt myself burying my hands in my body.] (live: 2s)[(stop:)$t[Well, not literally, but |close>[close].]]]

(click: ?close)[$t[I felt I was sticking my fingers into a kind of internal channel.]] (click: "channel")[$t[Like a |part>[basic part] of what I am.]] (click: ?part)[$t[A river for |life>[my life] to flow through.]] (click: ?life)[$t[And I found |something>[something] blocking the flow.]] (click: ?something)[$t[Something that could only be felt.] (live: 1s)[(stop:)$t[Like a faceless (link-reveal: "snake")[ $t[with the consistency of a slug](live: 2s)[(stop:)$t[. Dead]]].]]] (click: "Dead")[$t[I mean, inert, like an object(live: 2s)[(stop:)$t[, but aware of what was happening]].]] (click: "aware")[$t[It noticed me when I grabbed it.]] (click: "grabbed")[$t[It tried to slip through my fingers, but I |w>[wouldn’t] let it.]] (click: ?w)[$t[I threw it away and the river |ran>[ran] as it should.]]

(click: ?ran)[$t[It was like a dream, and when my husband woke me up Belona was sitting just like when we’d started. I was sprawled on the floor, sobbing.]]

(click: "sobbing")[$t[Like I said, I didn’t pray with her again after that. And I couldn’t have, because a few weeks later I became pregnant with Alma.]] (click: "Alma")[$tr[**[[(3/5)|three]]**]]

(click: ?ever)[$t[There were no complications in the pregnancy or the birth. Belona’s sister grew healthy and strong. Even as a baby, she had a vitality we rarely saw in Claro Largo. We called her Alma.]

](click: "vitality")[$t[She learned to (link-reveal: "walk")[$t[ and she learned to (link-reveal: "run")[$t[ and she learned to leave our sight without warning. Alma ran away often. She inherited my desire to |fly>[fly] in a way Belona never could]]]].]

](click: "into the woods")[$t[Running around Claro Largo had always been relatively safe, except for the woods.] (click: "except")[$t[We never knew |how>[how] the Takeover went down|p>[.]]] (click: ?how)[(replace: ?p)[$t[: the City was quieter but still busy, and the police kept monitoring the woods.]]] (click: "still busy")[$t[Surely they knew of us but didn’t have the resources or the |will>[will] to do something about it.]] (click: ?will)[$t[Our peace, however, depended on us not giving them a reason.]]

]<center>(click: "control")[$t[Alma would make her little trips into the woods whenever she could.] ](click: "the leader")[$t[We could never control her.] ](link: "admired")[$tr[The (link-reveal: "kids")[ $t[in Claro Largo]]] admired $tr[(link-reveal: "Alma")[$t[, and over the years she set up a gang and established herself as the leader]].]]</center>
(click: "a reason")[$t[We taught the youngest about the City and the cells so they could value the freedom they were born into.]] (click: "taught")[$t[With Alma this |worked>[worked] a little too well.]] (click: ?worked)[$t[She believed we *settled* for a certain life. That cherishing our freedom was a kind hypocrisy if we didn’t seek to *expand* it.]] (click: "expand")[$t[She didn’t know the City, so she took |life>[our life] in Claro Largo for granted.]] (click: ?life)[$t[But our life came at a (link-reveal: "cost")[$t[ and a bigger life comes at a |big>[bigger] cost](click: ?big)[$t[, I don’t think she |ever>[ever] got that]]].]]

(click: ?fly)[$t[The elders grew |worried>[worried].]] (click: ?worried)[$t[We wouldn’t stop her from talking, so we hatched a plan to take her off her followers’ minds.]] (click: "a plan")[$t[And we lost any hope of succeeding once Alma started coming back from her trips with news from |villages>[neighboring villages].]] (click: ?villages)[$tr[**[[(4/5)|four]]**]]

(click: "familia")[$t[Criamos a Belona como si fuera (link-reveal: "nuestra")[$t[, porque |era>[*era*] nuestra]].] (click: ?era)[$t[La vi ese día en la escuelita y me vi a mí misma.] (live: 2s)[(stop:)$t[Hablamos.] (live: 2s)[(stop:)$t[Me dijo que su familia había muerto en la Toma(click: "muerto")[$t[, que ella había visto]].]]]] (click: "visto")[$t[A veces hay tanta crueldad en el mundo…]]

](click: ?tuviera)[$t[Era muy introvertida.]] (click: "nada")[$t[No recuerdo que |tuviera>[tuviera] amigos.] (click: "introvertida")[$t[Los vecinos le prestaban libros y ella los devoraba.]] (click: "libros")[$t[No le iba particularmente bien en clase.]] (click: "particularmente")[$t[Mal tampoco.]]

](click: "vecinos")[$t[Apenas salía de casa.] (live: 1s)[(stop:)$t[Casi no recordaba la Ciudad.]] (click: "Casi")[$t[Creo que nunca apreció la libertad que teníamos en Claro Largo(click: "nunca")[$t[ porque no sabía lo que era que te la arrebataran]].]]

]<center>rezaba(click-replace: "rezaba")[$tr[Belona] rezaba $tr[seguido.]] (click: "seguido")[$t[Creo que eso es lo que hacía.]] (click: "Creo")[$t[Generalmente en Claro Largo nos gustaba que los jóvenes cultivaran su |fe>[fe] de chicos(click: ?fe)[$t[, pero lo que Belona describía de sus revelaciones internas siempre nos inquietó]].]] (click: "revelaciones")[$t[Creo que entendía el concepto de hablar con Dios(click: "entendía")[$t[, pero se sentaba sola, contemplativa, sin hablarle a nadie]].]] (click: "contemplativa")[$t[Supongo que *tenía* que hablar con alguien, consigo misma, o su familia.]]</center>
(click: "crueldad")[$t[Lo describía como explorar su propio ser.]] (click: "Lo describía")[$t[Cuando le pedías una imagen más clara, hablaba de enterrar las manos en sus entrañas buscando algo fundamental(click: "algo")[$t[, o buscándose a sí misma]].]] (click: "sí misma")[$t[Una vez le pregunté si alguna vez se había encontrado.]] (click: "encontrado")[$t[Me |contesto>[contestó] que lo que encontró es que no había nada que encontrar.]] (click: ?contesto)[$t[Muchas de estas conversaciones no las compartí con los demás mayores.]] (click: "mayores")[$t[Ya bastante sospechaban.]]

(click: "libertad")[$t[|trate>[Traté] de rezar con ella.]] (click: ?trate)[$t[Durante (link-reveal: "un mes")[$t[ o casi]].]] (click: "casi")[$t[Después dejé.] (live: 1s)[(stop:)$t[No me gustó, la verdad.]]] (click: "verdad")[$t[La última vez, creo que entendí algo de lo que Belona |decía>[decía].]] (click: ?decía)[$t[(link-reveal: "Lo de buscarse…")[ $t[Esperaba que lo de tocarse las entrañas fuera más metafórico(click: "Esperaba")[$t[, pero lo |senti>[sentí]]].]]]] (click: ?senti)[$t[Me sentí enterrando las manos en el cuerpo.] (live: 2s)[(stop:)$t[Bueno, no literalmente, pero |cerca>[casi].]]]

(click: ?cerca)[$t[Sentí que metía los dedos en una especie de canal interno.]] (click: "canal")[$t[Como una |parte>[parte básica] de lo que soy.]] (click: ?parte)[$t[Un río por el que fluía |vida>[mi vida].]] (click: ?vida)[$t[Y encontré |algo>[algo] obstruyendo el paso del agua.]] (click: ?algo)[$t[Algo que sólo se podía sentir.] (live: 1s)[(stop:)$t[Como una víbora sin cara(click: "víbora")[ $t[con la consistencia de una babosa](live: 2s)[(stop:)$t[. Muerta]]].]]] (click: "Muerta")[$t[Es decir, inerte, como un objeto(live: 2s)[(stop:)$t[, pero se daba cuenta de lo que pasaba]].]] (click: "cuenta")[$t[Trató de escurrirse entre mis dedos, pero |no>[no] la dejé.]] (click: ?no)[$t[La arranqué de donde estaba y el río empezó a |correr>[correr] como debía.]]

(click: ?correr)[$t[Fue como un sueño, y cuando mi esposo me despertó Belona estaba sentada como cuando habíamos empezado. Yo estaba desparramada en el suelo, llorando a los gritos.]]

(click: "llorando")[$t[Como dije, no volví a rezar con ella. Y no hubiera podido, porque unas semanas más tarde quedé embarazada de Alma.]] (click: "Alma")[$tr[**[[(3/5)|tres]]**]]

(click: ?entendiera)[$t[Ni el embarazo ni el parto tuvieron complicaciones. La hermana de Belona creció sana y fuerte. De muy beba demostró una vitalidad que en Claro Largo casi no se veía. La llamamos Alma.]

](click: "vitalidad")[$t[Aprendió a (link-reveal: "caminar")[$t[ y aprendió a (link-reveal: "correr")[$t[ y aprendió a irse de nuestra vista sin avisar. Alma se escapaba seguido. Heredó mis ganas de |volar>[volar] de una manera que Belona nunca pudo]]]].]

](click: "al bosque")[$t[Dar vueltas por Claro Largo siempre fue relativamente seguro, salvo por los bosques.] (click: "salvo")[$t[Nunca supimos |que>[qué] fue de la Toma|p>[.]]] (click: ?que)[(replace: ?p)[$t[: la Ciudad estaba más callada pero todavía operaba, y la policía seguía monitoreando los bosques.]]] (click: "todavía operaba")[$t[Seguro sabían de nosotros pero no tenían los recursos ni las |ganas>[ganas] de hacer algo al respecto.]] (click: ?ganas)[$t[Nuestra paz, sin embargo, dependía de que no les diéramos una razón.]]

]<center>(click: "controlarla")[$t[Alma hacía sus excursiones al bosque siempre que podía.] ](click: "líder")[$t[Nunca pudimos controlarla.] ](link: "admiraban")[$tr[Los (link-reveal: "chicos")[ $t[en Claro Largo]]] admiraban $tr[a (link-reveal: "Alma")[$t[, y con los años fue armando una banda y se estableció como una especie de líder]].]]</center>
(click: "una razón")[$t[A los más jóvenes les enseñábamos sobre sobre la Ciudad y las celdas para que pudieran valorar la libertad en la que habían nacido.]] (click: "enseñábamos")[$t[Con Alma |funciono>[funcionó] demasiado bien.]] (click: ?funciono)[$t[Ella creía que nos habíamos *conformado* con una cierta vida. Que atesorar nuestra libertad era una especie de hipocresía si no intentábamos *expandirla*.]] (click: "expandirla")[$t[No conocía la Ciudad, así que daba |vida>[nuestra vida] en Claro Largo por sentado.]] (click: ?vida)[$t[Pero nuestra vida había llegado a un (link-reveal: "precio")[$t[ y una vida más grande tiene un precio |mayor>[*mayor*]](click: ?mayor)[$t[, no creo que ella lo |entendiera>[entendiera]]]].]]

(click: ?volar)[$t[Los mayores estábamos |preocupados>[preocupados].]] (click: ?preocupados)[$t[No le íbamos a impedir que hablara, así que urdimos un plan para arrebatarle la admiración de sus seguidores.]] (click: "un plan")[$t[Y perdimos cualquier esperanza de tener éxito cuando Alma empezó a volver de sus excursiones con noticias de |pueblos>[pueblos vecinos].]] (click: ?pueblos)[$tr[**[[(4/5)|cuatro]]**]]
